		<h1><a name="billing" style="text-decoration: none;">Billing</a></h1>


			<div class="accordion-group">
				<div class="accordion-heading"><a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion10" href="#collapseTen">How Will I Be Billed?</a>
				</div>
				<div id="collapseTen" class="accordion-body collapse">
					<div class="accordion-inner">You will be billed by your new energy provider. Your new supplier will you through the straightfoward onboarding process and you'll be able to set up your account and billing preferences - electonic or paper bills.</div>
				</div>
			</div>


			<div class="accordion-group">
				<div class="accordion-heading"><a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion11" href="#collapseEleven">When Will I receive My First Bill?</a>
				</div>
				<div id="collapseEleven" class="accordion-body collapse">
					<div class="accordion-inner">You will receive your first bill between 2 and 6 weeks after initiating your service. Service change is not immediate, and can sometimes take up to 30 days for your Greenir service provider to officially begin.</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="accordion-group">
